item.description: I know many people at Squire's and also the DJ. We always have a lot of fun. After speaking with other meet up people, I realize they would like this venue. You don't have to sing to come along and have fun with us. It is always lots of laughs. And lots of good singers, too!
item.how_to_find_us: We will be sitting in the Resturant side with a Meet up sign
item.name: Karaoke at Squire White's Resturant
